All I need is You,
Jesus, all I need is You.
You are the the Source of all I need;
All I need is You!


All I want is You,
Jesus, all I want is You.
You are the the Source of all I need;
All I want is You!


My only hope is You,
Lord, my only hope is You.
You are the the Source of all I need;
My only hope is You!


All I need is You,
Jesus, all I need is You.
You are the the Source of all I need;
All I need is You!

